				<outline text="I can't overstate how much I hate this message, and the friction of dealing with it: &quot;This Apple ID has been locked for security reasons. Visit iForgot to reset your account (https://t.co/5tYlujdvwQ).&quot; BTW, I didn't forget, and neither @apple nor I know why this keeps happening." type="tweet" created="Fri, 18 Jun 2021 13:47:17 GMT" tweetId="1405884827036008450" urltweet="https://twitter.com/dsearls/status/1405884827036008450" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="dsearls" />
